 ('4', '4', 'en_us', 'About', 'About', '<p><img src=\"{asset:15:url}\" alt=\"profile.jpg#asset:15\" />Hi, I\'m Tyler. I\'m a <a href=\"http://github.com/tylerreckart\" target=\"_blank\">front-end developer</a>, <a href=\"http://dribbble.com/tylerreckart\">designer</a>, not at all professional skateboarder, and comic book enthusiast. I think a lot about how to make tools that <a href=\"http://github.com/tylerreckart/odin\" target=\"_blank\">improve your workflow</a> and make you more productive. I like to work with languages and tools like Javascript, Twig, and Elm, and I\'m constantly exploring other languages and tools for making the web awesome. Currently, I\'m exploring the world of functional programming through Haskell.<br /></p>\n\n\n\n<p>I currently work with the awesome team at <a href=\"http://authenticff.com\">Authentic Form &amp; Function</a>. We\'re a distributed team embodying and shaping the principals of remote work. Read more about us on our company <a href=\"http://authenticff.com/journal\" target=\"_blank\">journal</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><br /></p>', NULL, NULL, '2016-05-25 22:20:00', '2016-06-04 18:18:07', 'e2a1cccd-539e-4e9e-babe-b5da4336a8ab'),
