 ('1', '17', 'en_us', 'Odin', '<p>Odin is a zsh shell for git focused development. It includes (opinionated) configuration files for git, tmux, as well as vim in order to get you set up in a productive development environment. Check out the project on <a href=\"http://github.com/tylerreckart/odin\">github</a>.<br /></p>', '2016-05-27 00:25:38', '2016-06-13 12:19:57', '3b978383-671a-4d7f-933a-cf725f7bbb93'),
 ('2', '22', 'en_us', 'Tenor', '<p>Tenor started as an attempt to reconstruct Instapaper with React.js. It was open sourced in the fall of 2015, and I have since taken the repository offline in order to restructure how it works. I am currently rebuilding the application with Elm as well as rewriting and optimizing the HTML Parsing algorithm behind it. I hope to rerelease it by the end of this year. Follow any updates on twitter <a href=\"http://twitter.com/tylerreckart\" target=\"_blank\">@tylerreckart</a>.</p>', '2016-05-31 13:34:17', '2016-06-13 12:19:57', 'ab21f867-7aea-43ae-81ac-40bc750a15e3');



